cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SY. 

The paper is about using reinforcement learning to automatically generate high-performing CNN architectures for image classification tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves the use of neural networks, which could place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the use of reinforcement learning could also place it in cs.SY (Systems and Control).
